{"tid":1774834,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高院終院先後遭縱火 鐵閘被熏黑","createTime":"2019-12-08T13:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T13:17:24.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e239c7b682bfddaeee8704cfb7a78f7e1d824c65","tid":1774834,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DKF5eZixYZRSK_qZmVb3lA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191208a183338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDKF5eZixYZRSK_qZmVb3lA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191208a183338.jpg&h=5fd13b06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事發在下午6時許，金鐘高等法院其中一個入口鐵閘起火，現場冒出火光，半個鐵閘被熏黑，地上留有玻璃碎片及毛巾，消防接報到場以滅火筒救熄。據了解，事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上約7時，中環終審法院被人投擲懷疑燃燒彈，有在場人士其後用水將其救熄。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>人民日報再批港法院禁蒙面法裁決：必須嚴懲所有暴徒</strong><br />\n<strong>法工委港澳辦抨擊香港高院《禁蒙面法》「違憲」裁決</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-50470042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-50470042&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=53f5b564\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-50470042&h=b854991d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-50470042</a>"}]}